<a target="_blank" href="http://isux.tencent.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/20150701094655618.png"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-19963" src="http://isux.tencent.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/20150701094655618-590x929.png" alt="2015智能可穿戴市场白皮书" alt="wearable (1)" width="590" height="929" /></a> <a target="_blank" href="http://isux.tencent.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/20150701094657550.png"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-19964" src="http://isux.tencent.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/20150701094657550-590x929.png" alt="2015智能可穿戴市场白皮书" alt="wearable (2)" width="590" height="929" /></a> <a target="_blank" href="http://isux.tencent.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/20150701094659308.png"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-19965" src="http://isux.tencent.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/20150701094659308-590x929.png" alt="2015智能可穿戴市场白皮书" alt="wearable (3)" width="590" height="929" /></a> <a target="_blank" href="http://isux.tencent.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/201507010947019.png"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-19966" src="http://isux.tencent.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/201507010947019-590x929.png" alt="2015智能可穿戴市场白皮书" alt="wearable (4)" width="590" height="929" /></a> <a target="_blank" href="http://isux.tencent.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/20150701094702729.png"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-19967" src="http://isux.tencent.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/20150701094702729-590x929.png" alt="2015智能可穿戴市场白皮书" alt="wearable (5)" width="590" height="929" /></a> <a target="_blank" href="http://isux.tencent.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/20150701094704388.png"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-19968" src="http://isux.tencent.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/20150701094704388-590x929.png" alt="2015智能可穿戴市场白皮书" alt="wearable (6)" width="590" height="929" /></a> <a target="_blank" href="http://isux.tencent.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/20150701094706209.png"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-19969" src="ht