2" src="http://isux.tencent.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/20150701094730477-590x929.png" alt="2015智能可穿戴市场白皮书" alt="wearable (20)" width="590" height="929" /></a> <a target="_blank" href="http://isux.tencent.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/20150701094732463.png"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-19983" src="http://isux.tencent.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/20150701094732463-590x929.png" alt="2015智能可穿戴市场白皮书" alt="wearable (21)" width="590" height="929" /></a> <a target="_blank" href="http://isux.tencent.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/20150701094734329.png"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-19984" src="http://isux.tencent.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/20150701094734329-590x929.png" alt="2015智能可穿戴市场白皮书" alt="wearable (22)" width="590" height="929" /></a> <a target="_blank" href="http://isux.tencent.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/20150701094736183.png"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-19985" src="http://isux.tencent.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/20150701094736183-590x929.png" alt="2015智能可穿戴市场白皮书" alt="wearable (23)" width="590" height="929" /></a> <a target="_blank" href="http://isux.tencent.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/2015070109473854.png"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-19986" src="http://isux.tencent.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/2015070109473854-590x929.png" alt="2015智能可穿戴市场白皮书" alt="wearable (24)" width="590" height="929" /></a> <a target="_blank" href="http://isux.tencent.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/20150701094739978.png"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-19987" src="http://isux.tencent.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/20150701094739978-590x929.png" alt="2015智能可穿戴市场白皮书" alt="wearable (25)" width="590" height="929" /></a></p>
