<h2><strong>03   品牌色   BRAND COLOR</strong></h2>
<p><strong><a target="_blank" href="http://isux.tencent.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/20150625162447403.png"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-19931" src="http://isux.tencent.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/20150625162447403.png" alt="《黑x金》企鹅FM品牌24小时诞生记" alt="1434710487_47_w960_h671[1]" width="960" height="671" /></a></strong></p>
