</a>iOS Human Interface Guidelines &#8211; <a target="_blank" href="https://developer.apple.com/library/prerelease/ios/documentation/UserExperience/Conceptual/MobileHIG/AppExtensions.html#//apple_ref/doc/uid/TP40006556-CH67-SW4" target="_blank">Today Widgets</a></p>
